{{Top|leg}}
'''Sommin City''' was the [[Capital/Legends|capital]] [[City/Legends|city]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Seltos]]. The government building was named [[Freedom Hall]], and it was the location of the [[Star Hotel]] and [[12 Galactar Route]].<ref name="FSS">{{WEGCite|story=Freedom Strike Seltos (adventure)|book=Twin Stars of Kira (sourcebook)}}</ref> It was home to the largest group of [[Tarro]] remnants in [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]], number seven individuals.<ref name="GG12">''[[Galaxy Guide 12: Aliens — Enemies and Allies]]''</ref>

==Behind the scenes==
The city is referred to as '''Somin City''' in ''[[Galaxy Guide 12: Aliens — Enemies and Allies]]''.

